      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Letters relating chiefly to the sale, leasing, and development of land, to lumbering,
            and to political and social life in Chenango County, New York. Correspondents include
            Colonel Cady, Obadiah German, Abraham R. Lawrence, Caleb Lawrence, W.T. Lawrence, Robert
            L. Livingston, Theodore Sill, John Sudam, Simon G. Throop, Gerrit Van Wagenen, and
            Marinus Willett.</p>
      </scopecontent>
